<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 13:25:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普言论引发新的伊朗战争担忧，比特币走弱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-08/bitcoin-btc-weakens-as-trump-s-remarks-raise-fresh-iran-war-concerns</link><description>由于新的地缘政治紧张局势扰乱了数字资产市场，比特币暴跌，掩盖了本周早些时候对 Strategy Inc. 最新出售该代币的温和反应。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3NyoDhmXESA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 09:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-08/bitcoin-btc-weakens-as-trump-s-remarks-raise-fresh-iran-war-concerns</guid></item><item><title>委内瑞拉地震后，稳定币变成了援助铁路</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-07-07/venezuela-quakes-turn-stablecoins-into-emergency-aid-rails</link><description>稳定币正在成为委内瑞拉紧急援助的关键渠道。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iIOWJ1x3mSvM/v7/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-07-07/venezuela-quakes-turn-stablecoins-into-emergency-aid-rails</guid></item><item><title>量子会破解加密吗？为什么比特币所有者担心</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-07/will-quantum-computers-hack-bitcoin-and-other-cryptocurrencies</link><description>&lt;p&gt;如果量子计算变得更加先进，多达 4700 亿美元的比特币可能面临风险&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izhKEHo1FJGs/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 14:29:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-07/will-quantum-computers-hack-bitcoin-and-other-cryptocurrencies</guid></item><item><title>Tether 前首席信息官计划出售稳定币巨头的股份</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-06/tether-s-former-cio-plans-sale-of-stake-in-stablecoin-giant</link><description>据知情人士透露，今年早些时候一直负责监督稳定币巨头 Tether Holdings SA 投资组合的理查德·希思科特 (Richard Heathcote) 正计划出售该公司的少量股份。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iwnI3erUSOao/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 20:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-06/tether-s-former-cio-plans-sale-of-stake-in-stablecoin-giant</guid></item><item><title>随着各部门寻求控制，特朗普比特币储备面临障碍</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-06/trump-bitcoin-reserve-faces-hurdles-as-departments-seek-control</link><description>特朗普政府创建比特币战略储备的计划因两个政府部门竞相管理而变得复杂，同时还存在关于哪个政府部门拥有这样做的法律权力的问题。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9LKne21LdZU/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 18:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-06/trump-bitcoin-reserve-faces-hurdles-as-departments-seek-control</guid></item></channel></rss>